org.apereo.cas.services

接口 RegisteredService

  • 所有超级接口:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<RegisteredService>, java.io.Serializable

    public interface RegisteredService
extends java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<RegisteredService>
    Interface for a service that can be registered by the Services Management interface.
    从以下版本开始:
    3.1

    • 字段概要

      字段 
      限定符和类型 字段和说明
      static long INITIAL_IDENTIFIER_VALUE
      Initial ID value of newly created (but not persisted) registered service.

      • getProxyPolicy

        RegisteredServiceProxyPolicy getProxyPolicy()
        Get the proxy policy rules for this service.
        返回:
        the proxy policy

      • getServiceId

        java.lang.String getServiceId()
        The unique identifier for this service.
        返回:
        the unique identifier for this service.

      • getId

        long getId()
        The numeric identifier for this service. Implementations are expected to initialize the id with the value of INITIAL_IDENTIFIER_VALUE.
        返回:
        the numeric identifier for this service.

      • getName

        java.lang.String getName()
        Returns the name of the service.
        返回:
        the name of the service.

      • getTheme

        java.lang.String getTheme()
        Returns a short theme name. Services do not need to have unique theme names.
        返回:
        the theme name associated with this service.

      • getDescription

        java.lang.String getDescription()
        Returns the description of the service.
        返回:
        the description of the service.

      • getEvaluationOrder

        int getEvaluationOrder()
        Gets the relative evaluation order of this service when determining matches.
        返回:
        Evaluation order relative to other registered services. Services with lower values will be evaluated for a match before others.

      • setEvaluationOrder

        void setEvaluationOrder(int evaluationOrder)
        Sets the relative evaluation order of this service when determining matches.
        参数:
        evaluationOrder - the service evaluation order

      • getUsernameAttributeProvider

        RegisteredServiceUsernameAttributeProvider getUsernameAttributeProvider()
        Get the name of the attribute this service prefers to consume as username.
        返回:
        an instance of RegisteredServiceUsernameAttributeProvider

      • getMultifactorPolicy

        RegisteredServiceMultifactorPolicy getMultifactorPolicy()
        Gets authentication policy.
        返回:
        the authentication policy

      • getRequiredHandlers

        java.util.Set<java.lang.String> getRequiredHandlers()
        Gets the set of handler names that must successfully authenticate credentials in order to access the service. An empty set indicates that there are no requirements on particular authentication handlers; any will suffice.
        返回:
        Non -null set of required handler names.

      • getAccessStrategy

        RegisteredServiceAccessStrategy getAccessStrategy()
        Gets the access strategy that decides whether this registered service is able to proceed with authentication requests.
        返回:
        the access strategy

      • matches

        boolean matches(org.apereo.cas.authentication.principal.Service service)
        Returns whether the service matches the registered service.

        Note, as of 3.1.2, matches are case insensitive.

        参数:
        service - the service to match.
        返回:
        true if they match, false otherwise.

      • matches

        boolean matches(java.lang.String serviceId)
        Returns whether the service id matches the registered service.
        参数:
        serviceId - the service id to match.
        返回:
        true if they match, false otherwise.

                 throws java.lang.CloneNotSupportedException

      • getLogo

        java.lang.String getLogo()
        Gets the logo image associated with this service. The image mostly is served on the user interface to identify this requesting service during authentication.
        返回:
        URL of the image
        从以下版本开始:
        4.1

      • getInformationUrl

        java.lang.String getInformationUrl()
        Describes the canonical information url where this service is advertised and may provide help/guidance.
        返回:
        the info url.

      • getPrivacyUrl

        java.lang.String getPrivacyUrl()
        Links to the privacy policy of this service, if any.
        返回:
        the link to privacy policy

      • getLogoutUrl

        java.net.URL getLogoutUrl()
        Identifies the logout url that that will be invoked upon sending single-logout callback notifications. This is an optional setting. When undefined, the service url as is defined by getServiceId() will be used to handle logout invocations.
        返回:
        the logout url for this service
        从以下版本开始:
        4.1

      • getPublicKey

        RegisteredServicePublicKey getPublicKey()
        Gets the public key associated with this service that is used to authorize the request by encrypting certain elements and attributes in the CAS validation protocol response, such as the PGT.
        返回:
        the public key instance used to authorize the request
        从以下版本开始:
        4.1

      • getProperties

        java.util.Map<java.lang.String,RegisteredServiceProperty> getProperties()
        Describes extra metadata about the service; custom fields that could be used by submodules implementing additional behavior on a per-service basis.
        返回:
        map of custom metadata.
        从以下版本开始:
        4.2
